This is a basic PAM module bundled with a basic application to demonstrate 2-step authentification for CS3235 project

It consists of 4 files:

* Makefile : to automate builing and cleaning
* basic_pam.c : source file for the PAM module
* test.c : test application using the basic_pam module
* test.pamconf : configuration file for test

To setup the module and build the application: type "make".
To remove temporary files and the module: type "make clean".
It is assumed that you have administrating priliveges and that sudo is installed in your system.

Once targets have been built, the test application will reside in the bin folder.
